'''"Name it, Claim it"''' is a [[catch phrase]] of the [[Word of faith|Word faith movement]]. Other common "Positive confession" phrases used to express the same sentiment include:
* "What I confess, I possess." &mdash; [[E.W. Kenyon]]
* "Say it; do it; receive it; tell it." &mdash; [[Kenneth E. Hagin|Kenneth Hagin]]

